		<td style="font-family: Trebuchet MS; font-size: 8pt; color: #FFFFFF; font-weight: bold; text-align: left; background-color: #333333; border-left: 2px solid #000000; border-right: 2px solid #FFFFFF; border-top: 2px solid #000000; border-bottom: 2px solid #FFFFFF">
			<br>&nbsp;<u><i><font color="#FFFF00">MAIN GAME CONTROLS:</font></i></u><br>
                  &nbsp; Move between answers:
                  <font color="#00FF00">&nbsp;D-Pad</font>
				  <br>&nbsp; Select answer -
                  <font color="#00FF00">&nbsp;Circle Button</font>
				  <br>&nbsp; Fast forward text -
                  <font color="#00FF00">&nbsp;L2 Button</font>
				  <br>&nbsp; Show / Hide text -
                  <font color="#00FF00">&nbsp;Select Button</font><br>
			<br>&nbsp;<u><i><font color="#FFFF00">RUNNING & WEIGHTLIFTING MINI GAMES CONTROLS:</font></i></u><br>
                  &nbsp; Run faster or weightlift -
                  <font color="#00FF00">&nbsp;Press Circle Button when the trainer gives the order</font><br>
			<br>&nbsp;<u><i><font color="#FFFF00">COMB HAIR MINI GAME CONTROLS:</font></i></u><br>
                  &nbsp; Comb -
                  <font color="#00FF00">&nbsp;Press Circle Button + D-Pad up at the proper time</font><br>
			<br>&nbsp;<u><i><font color="#FFFF00">GRAB BALL MINI GAME CONTROLS:</font></i></u><br>
                  &nbsp; Grab ball -
                  <font color="#00FF00">&nbsp;Press Circle Button + D-Pad up at the proper time</font><br>
			<br>&nbsp;<u><i><font color="#FFFF00">STUDY & COOKING MINI GAMES CONTROLS:</font></i></u><br>
                  &nbsp; Study or cook -
                  <font color="#00FF00">&nbsp;Press Circle Button at the proper time</font><br>
			<br>&nbsp;<u><i><font color="#FFFF00">DURING MATCHS CONTROLS:</font></i></u><br>
                  &nbsp; Hit ball -
                  <font color="#00FF00">&nbsp;Press Circle Button + D-Pad direction to hit the ball</font>
                  <br>&nbsp; Call time -
                  <font color="#00FF00">&nbsp;Triangle Button</font>
                  <br>&nbsp; Cancel action -
                  <font color="#00FF00">&nbsp;X Button</font>
                  <br>&nbsp; Pause game -
                  <font color="#00FF00">&nbsp;Start Button</font><br><br>				  
				  &nbsp;</td>
	 </tr>
